				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Anyone found or made a countdown/timer for their bot?
<br />

<br />
So that users can /tell bot timer 15
<br />

<br />
and then 15 minutes later the bot send them a tell "Your timer is up"
<br />

<br />
doing /tell bot timer 60 would make the bot send a tell 1 hour later.
<br />

<br />
Anyone seen anything like this?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
