				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ok, this is what ethernal (megabio) helped me with so far:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">if&#40;$words&#91;0&#93; == &quot;timer&quot;&#41;&#123;
<br />

<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$times&#91;$charName&#93;&#91;&quot;time&quot;&#93; = time&#40;&#41;; 
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$times&#91;$charName&#93;&#91;&quot;timer&quot;&#93; = &#40;$words&#91;1&#93;*60&#41;; 
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$times&#91;$charName&#93;&#91;&quot;action&quot;&#93; = &#40;$words&#91;2&#93;&#41;; 
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$seconds = $words&#91;1&#93;*60;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;echo &quot;$charName started a timer on $seconds seconds code = $substance\n&quot;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$message = $color&#91;&quot;lblue&quot;&#93; . &quot;&#58;&#58; &quot; . $color&#91;&quot;lgrey&quot;&#93; . &quot; Ok! Timer set&quot;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$aoc-&gt;send_tell&#40;$charName, $message&#41;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
<br />
